&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-LAVO-NIGHTCLUB-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-8386&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NYC-LAVO-NIGHTCLUB-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;NYC- LAVO NIGHTCLUB- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;163&quot; height=&quot;55&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;LAVO New York is the east coast incarnation of the famed Las Vegas location. Attracting a stylish, metropolitan crowd guests will find the same glitz and glamour of Las Vegas in addition to New York City sophistication. An elevated VIP area surrounds a sunken dance floor. Progressive house music electrifies this 6000 square foot venue. Upscale, trendy attire. Collared Shirts and Dress Shoes for gentlemen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact LAVO via email only at dinersclubnyc@taogroup.com to book your reservation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Nightlife Access to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention that the booking is for a reservation at LAVO New York&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to attend, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ages 21 &amp;amp; Over. ID must be provided.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit is applicable for up to 2 guests in total.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dress code will be strictly enforced. Upscale, trendy. Collared Shirts and Dress Shoes for gentlemen. No sneakers, hats, boots, athletic wear, or shorts. Management reserves the right to refuse entry to guests due to visible intoxication, lack of proper ID, failure to adhere to dress code, or capacity limits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access is granted only with reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve seating is ONLY with bottle service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late arrivals past midnight will be required to pay any required cover charges, despite having a reservation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Nightlife Access.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Diners Club Card must be used for payment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Nightlife Access benefit may not be combined with other offers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Nightclub/Lounge merchant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations&nbsp;based on availability at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Nightclub/lounge participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blackout dates may apply due to event buyouts. Special event/DJs may incur a charge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

